Package org.dellroad.stuff.vaadin24.field

Annotation Interface FieldBuilder.ListBox

Enclosing class:
FieldBuilder<T>
@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) @Documented public static @interface FieldBuilder.ListBox
Specifies how a Java bean property should be edited using a ListBox.

  • Element Details

    • implementation

      Class<? extends ListBox> implementation
      Get the sub-type of ListBox that will edit the property.

      This property allows custom widget subclasses to be used.

      The specified type must have a public constructor that takes either no arguments, or one FieldBuilderContext.

      Returns:
      field type
      Default:
      com.vaadin.flow.component.listbox.ListBox.class

    • styleProperties

      String[] styleProperties
      Specify CSS properties to be set via Style.set().

      The array value consists of name, value pairs. If the array has odd length, the last element is ignored.

      Returns:
      zero or more style property name, value pairs
      See Also:
      • Style
      • HasStyle
      Default:
      {}
